# Prompt Logging

- After every request, append an entry to `logs/ai-prompts/YYYY-MM-DD.md` (create if missing).
- Entry format: `YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm UTC | USER | "<prompt>" | files: path1,path2 | tests: <tests or none>`
- Use initials/short user id for USER (ask if unknown).
- If no files changed, use `files: none`. If no tests run, use `tests: none`.
- Keep entries ASCII and single-line.
